Package alix.util

Class IntPair

java.lang.Object
alix.util.IntPair
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<IntPair>
public class IntPair
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<IntPair>
A mutable pair of ints. Works well as a key for a HashMap (hascode() implemented), comparable is good for perfs in buckets. After test, concating ints in longs is not more efficient in HashMap.
Author:
glorieux-f
